Review Text: I have been buying coffee from Naked for more than 8 years, maybe closer to 10? I used to regularly frequent the café on little Bourke many moons ago I've never had such lovable and reliable coffee like that before or since. …

Name: Naked Espresso
Review Text: Great coffee beans, great service, great voice knowledge and advise-  what can i say JUST GREAT!

Name: Naked Espresso
Review Text: What's not to love: local to Bayside, and some of the best coffee beans I've had! I'd give them 6 stars (a bonus star for hand delivering!), but Google won't let me.

Name: Naked Espresso
Review Text: Every time I go to Melbourne I keep returning to this place just to make sure that I wasn't imagining it. …

Review Text: I've lived in the city for 10 years. I drink a lot of coffee. I go to little bean blue, brother and 65 degrees. These are the best consistently good coffee places in the city.  I've now had 3 'magic' coffees from naked espresso, all …

Name: Naked Espresso
Review Text: Fantastic coffee, lovely barista, great artwork. We were just looking for a quick coffee in the area but left with packs of beans too 😂👍🏼👍🏼

Name: Naked Espresso
Review Text: Great spot to swing by before work for my caffeine fix. Staff are friendly and always up for a chat. Added bonus for a small selection of products for home use too.

Name: Naked Espresso
Review Text: Small, quirky name that's hard to forget. Just like the coffee! I ordered a standard latte to have in. I tell you I could almost stand my spoon in it, as it was so rich....One of the best I have had in the CBD

Name: Naked Espresso
Review Text: Literally the best coffee in Australia, if not the world. I can't start my day without a nice strong coffee from Naked!

Name: Naked Espresso
Review Text: Wonderful coffee, great if you’re in the area, hospitable staff which were down to chat about coffee.

Review Text: I had a pretty good espresso and a nice chat but when asking where BBB was you sent me on a wild goose chase?? I didnt realize how close it was.
